       *OET do file
*By Phil Tian

clear all

set mem 250m
set maxvar 32000
set matsize 2000
set more off

capture log close
log using "OET_log", replace
use oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta, clear

gen psexpectation_

program define OET_ML
args lnf lngamma lnfn tao1 tao2 tao3 tao4 tao5

tempvar prob1 prob2 prob3 prob4 prob5 probsum
tempvar ps p01 p02 p03 p04 p05 z dz1 dz2 dz p
tempvar lnf1 lnf2 lnf3 lnf4 lnf5
tempvar dM

*define the p0 probabilities

gen double `probsum'=exp(`tao1')+exp(`tao2')+exp(`tao3')+exp(`tao4')+exp(`tao5')
gen double `prob1'= exp(`tao1')/`probsum'
gen double `prob2'= exp(`tao2')/`probsum'
gen double `prob3'= exp(`tao3')/`probsum'
gen double `prob4'= exp(`tao4')/`probsum'
gen double `prob5'= exp(`tao5')/`probsum'
scalar `p01'=0.1
scalar `p02'=0.2
scalar `p03'=0.3
scalar `p04'=0.4
scalar `p05'=0.5

gen `ps'= $ML_y1
gen `p'= winpc_r

gen double `z'=(`ps'^(1/exp(`lngamma')))/(`ps'^(1/exp(`lngamma'))+(1-`ps')^(1/exp(`lngamma')))
gen double `dz1'=(1/exp(`lngamma'))*`ps'^(1/exp(`lngamma')-1)*(1-`ps')^(1/exp(`lngamma'))+`ps'^(1/exp(`lngamma'))*(1/exp(`lngamma'))*(1-`ps')^(1/exp(`lngamma')-1)
gen double `dz2'=(`ps'^(1/exp(`lngamma'))+(1-`ps')^(1/exp(`lngamma')))^2
gen double `dz'=`dz1'/`dz2'

gen double `dM'=(1/`z')*`dz'+(1/(1-`z'))*`dz'

gen double `lnf1'=normalden(ln(ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p01'*exp(`lnfn')))*(1/ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p01'*exp(`lnfn'))*`dM'*`prob1'
gen double `lnf2'=normalden(ln(ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p02'*exp(`lnfn')))*(1/ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p02'*exp(`lnfn'))*`dM'*`prob2'
gen double `lnf3'=normalden(ln(ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p03'*exp(`lnfn')))*(1/ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p03'*exp(`lnfn'))*`dM'*`prob3'
gen double `lnf4'=normalden(ln(ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p04'*exp(`lnfn')))*(1/ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p04'*exp(`lnfn'))*`dM'*`prob4'
gen double `lnf5'=normalden(ln(ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p05'*exp(`lnfn')))*(1/ln(`z')-ln(1-`z')-`p05'*exp(`lnfn'))*`dM'*`prob5'

quietly replace `lnf'=`lnf1'+`lnf2'+`lnf3'+`lnf4'+`lnf5'

end

ml model lf OET_ML (lngamma: psexpectation_r=bet earnings sdwin shistakes slostakes swealth) (lnfn: psexpectation_r=pitstopnum bet earnings sdwin shistakes slostakes swealth) (tao1:) (tao2:) (tao3:) (tao4:) (tao5:)
